        <div class="pub-info">
          <h3 class="pub-title">AlignedGen: Aligning Style Across Generated Images</h3>
          <p class="pub-authors"><span class="highlight-me">Jiexuan Zhang</span>, Yiheng Du, Qian Wang, Weiqi Li, Yu Gu, Jian Zhang</p>
          <p class="pub-venue"><em>NeurIPS</em>, 2025</p>
          <div class="pub-links">
            <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2509.17088/">arXiv</a> /
            <a href="https://jiexuanz.github.io/AlignedGen/">Project Page</a> /
            <a href="https://github.com/Jiexuanz/AlignedGen">Code</a>
            <span class="pub-stat github-stars" data-github-repo="Jiexuanz/AlignedGen" style="display:none;"></span>
            <span class="pub-stat citation-count" data-arxiv-id="2509.17088" style="display:none;"></span>
          </div>
          <p class="pub-desc">Aligning style across multiple generated images with reference-based diffusion approach.</p>
        </div>
